'''亞伯拉罕·“阿維”·勒布'''（{{lang-en|Abraham "Avi" Loeb}}；{{lang-he|אברהם (אבי) לייב}}；{{bd|1962年|2月26日|}}）是一名[[以色列|以色列]]裔[[美國|美國]][[理論物理學家|理論物理學家]]，從事[[天體物理學|天體物理學]]和[[宇宙學|宇宙學]]研究。他是[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]目前為止任期最久的[[天文學|天文學]]系主任（2011年至2020年），哈佛大學{{tsl|en|Black Hole Initiative|黑洞倡議}}的創始主任（自2016年起）和[[哈佛-史密松天體物理中心|哈佛-史密松天體物理中心]]的理論與計算研究所所長（自2007年起）。 <ref name="BioITC">{{cite web |title=Avi Loeb |url=https://itc.cfa.harvard.edu/people/avi-loeb |website=Institute for Theory and Computation @ Harvard University |publisher=Harvard University |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130004205/https://itc.cfa.harvard.edu/people/avi-loeb |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BioCFA">{{cite web |title=Professor Avi Loeb |url=https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/~loeb |website=Harvard & Smithsonian Center For Astronomy |publisher=Harvard University |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213033438/https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/~loeb/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BioBHI">{{cite web |title=Abraham (Avi) Loeb |url=https://bhi.fas.harvard.edu/people/avi-loeb |website=Black Hole Initiative @ Harvard University |publisher=Harvard University |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207010442/https://bhi.fas.harvard.edu/people/avi-loeb |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Autobiography">{{cite web |last1=Loeb |first1=Avi |title=Autobiographical sketch |url=https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/~loeb/Loeb_Autobiography.pdf |website=Harvard University |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210130033435/https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/~loeb/Loeb_Autobiography.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CV">{{cite web |last1=Loeb |first1=Abraham |title=Curriculum Vitae of Abraham Loeb |url=https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/~loeb/vitae.pdf |website=Harvard University |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210129081619/https://www.cfa.harvard.edu/~loeb/vitae.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BioDepAstro">{{cite web |title=Avi Loeb |url=https://astronomy.fas.harvard.edu/people/avi-loeb |website=Department of Astronomy @ Harvard University |publisher=Harvard University |accessdate=2021-02-07 |archive-date=2021-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204200615/https://astronomy.fas.harvard.edu/people/avi-loeb |dead-url=no }}</ref>

